---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="SoftBuyDeals Privacy Policy — how we collect, use, and protect your information as an Amazon.in affiliate website.">
  <div class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mb-8">Last updated: June 27, 2026</p>

        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          SoftBuyDeals ("we," "our," or "us") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website <strong>softbuydeals.in</strong>. By using our website, you consent to the practices described in this policy.
        </p>

        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name and email address when you voluntarily subscribe to our newsletter or contact us.</li>
          <li><strong>Non-Personal Information:</strong> Browser type, device type, operating system, referring URLs, and browsing behaviour collected automatically through cookies and analytics.</li>
          <li><strong>Affiliate Tracking Data:</strong> When you click on affiliate links (including Amazon.in links), standard tracking data such as referral source and click timestamps are captured through the affiliate network.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
        <p>
          We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Remember your preferences (e.g., dark mode preference)</li>
          <li>Understand how you interact with our website</li>
          <li>Track affiliate referrals through the Amazon Associates Programme</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Amazon.in uses cookies to determine if a purchase was made through our affiliate links. These cookies are placed by Amazon and are subject to Amazon's own Privacy Policy. You can control cookie settings through your browser preferences.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Amazon Associates Programme</h2>
        <p>
          SoftBuyDeals is a participant in the <strong>Amazon Associates Programme</strong>, an affiliate advertising programme designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to Amazon.in. Amazon uses cookies to track visits from our site to Amazon.in and attribute qualifying purchases.
        </p>
        <p>
          As an Amazon Associate, we earn from qualifying purchases. This means that if you click on an affiliate link and make a purchase on Amazon.in, we may receive a small commission at no additional cost to you.
        </p>
        <p>
          For more information about how Amazon uses your data, please review the <a href="https://www.amazon.in/gp/help/customer/display.html?nodeId=GX7NJQ4ZB8MHFRNJ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Amazon.in Privacy Notice</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>5. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>To operate and maintain our website</li>
          <li>To track affiliate referrals and commissions</li>
          <li>To send periodic emails if you have subscribed to our newsletter</li>
          <li>To improve our content and product recommendations</li>
          <li>To analyse website traffic and user behaviour</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          We may use third-party service providers to help us operate our website and analyse usage. These third parties have access to your information only to perform specific tasks on our behalf and are obligated not to disclose or use it for any other purpose.
        </p>
        <p>
          When you click on an Amazon.in affiliate link, you leave our website and are subject to Amazon.in's privacy practices. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of Amazon.in or any other third-party sites.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          We implement reasonable security measures to protect your personal information. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Our website is not directed to children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If we become aware that a child has provided us with personal information, we will take steps to delete it.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          Depending on your location, you may have the right to:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access the personal information we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction or deletion of your personal information</li>
          <li>Opt out of cookies and tracking</li>
          <li>Unsubscribe from our newsletter at any time</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page with an updated revision date.
        </p>

        <h2>11. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@softbuydeals.in">support@softbuydeals.in</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
